        <iframe src="../../../../webcontent/html_activities/mean_median/mean_median.html" height="500" width="600"></iframe>
         <p>Click below the line to add an observation. The red arrow marks the median. The green
            arrow marks the mean. When the median and mean are equal, a single yellow arrow is
            shown. You can use the mouse to drag a point along the line. <!--Drag a point to the trash
            to remove it. -->Click on the trash to remove all points. Note that you can "stack" more
            than one point at the same location.</p>
        
      
